{
  "texts": [
    "Individual Agency involves acting independently on one's own.",
    "Proxy Agency involves acting on behalf of someone else.",
    "Shared Agency involves multiple individuals working together jointly towards a common goal.",
    "Here, we focus on Shared Agency between humans and AI and develop methods to measure and control Agency of AI vis-a-vis humans.",
    "Our goal is to develop a framework for measuring and controlling Agency in LLMs."
  ]
}